    "Additionally, we identify commercially active research institutions by their membership in the Association of University Technology Managers (AUTM), requiring at least 0.5 full-time equivalent (FTE) staff dedicated to technology transfer.",
    "These criteria yield 126 U.S. universities.",
    "Our results are robust to alternative delineations of our institutional sample, including all U.S. universities regardless of AUTM membership.",
